me cannot exceed gross profit') that prunes implausible reasoning paths early. When discrepancies arise, FinAuditNet triggers targeted retrieval of prior-year filings or peer benchmarks to assess abnormal deviations. Explanations are generated as traceable audit trails showing how each step complies with or violates financial logic, enabling regulators to validate both outcome and process. This design significantly enhances reliability in high-stakes environments such as SEC compliance and ESG reporting verification. By shifting from reactive verification to proactive auditing intelligence, FinAuditNet offers a new paradigm for trustworthy AI in finance.",
